text: Fenestra is a genus of grasshoppers in the subfamily Gomphocerinae with species found in South America. ==Species== The following species are recognised in the genus Fenestra: * Fenestra bohlsii Giglio-Tos, 1895 * Fenestra ensicorne Rehn, 1913 * Fenestra orientalis (Bruner, 1913) * Fenestra platyceps (Hebard, 1924) == References == Category:Acrididae
title: Fenestra (grasshopper)
